# Canonical portal URLs (EA / CTP)

## Production (ea-payments on Vercel)

| Purpose | URL |
|---------|-----|
| **Codex CTP “Consider the Possibilities™” intake (canonical)** | https://cc.efficiencyarchitects.online/ctp |
| Same deploy | https://efficiency-architects.vercel.app/ctp |
| Source | OneDrive `efficiency-architects` → `OperationalMRI.jsx` route `/ctp` |
| Do NOT confuse with | `https://efficiencyarchitects.online/ctp-intake` (ea-payments Discover wizard — different product) |
| Legacy MRI quiz on CRA | https://cc.efficiencyarchitects.online/operational-mri |
| **CTP Magnifi story entry** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/consider/selena |
| **Client portal login** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/portal/login |
| **EA portal home (new chrome)** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/portal/ea |
| **Demo CTP workspace** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/portal/demo-client/ctp |
| **One-click demo session (preferred entry)** | https://efficiencyarchitects.online/api/auth/demo-enter |

Funnel: `/consider/{slug}` → CTA → `/ctp-intake` (Discover wizard) → thank-you → portal.  
`/buy` is Website + Portal Starter — not CTP intake.

Also OK (same CTP app): `https://portal.efficiencyarchitects.online/...`

## Wrong surfaces (do not treat as CTP)

- `www.efficiencyarchitects.online` — often old Growth Portal / wrong Vercel project
- `cc.efficiencyarchitects.online` — Command Center / old LaunchPad
- Next Steps Pro “Portal unavailable” LaunchPad — not this app

## Local

- Login: http://localhost:3000/portal/login
- Prefer password sign-in when `RESEND_API_KEY` / OTP is not wired
- Do not use `/api/auth/demo-enter` locally if it redirects to production apex

## Local env needed for email OTP

`AIRTABLE_API_KEY` and `RESEND_API_KEY` in `.env.local` (restart `npm run dev` after adding).
